OL,3,CKiller 'punched and pushed warehouse
OL,4,Cworkers' a month before Nottingham
OL,5,Cattacks
OL,7,FTriple killer Valdo Calocane attacked
OL,8,Ftwo members of staff when he was
OL,9,Fworking at a warehouse, a month before
OL,10,Fhe killed three people in Nottingham,
OL,11,Fan inquiry has heard.
OL,13,FCalocane fatally stabbed University of
OL,14,FNottingham undergraduates Barnaby
OL,15,FWebber and Grace O'Malley-Kumar, both
OL,16,F19, and grandfather Ian Coates, 65,
OL,17,Fand attempted to kill three more
OL,18,Fpeople in the early hours of June 13
OL,19,F2023.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G1/5
