PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F374A1773220132
OL,3,CKiller 'punched and pushed warehouse
OL,4,Cworkers' a month before Nottingham
OL,5,Cattacks
OL,7,FA month before the killings, Calocane
OL,8,Fbegan working as an agency warehouse
OL,9,Foperative for logistics company Arvato
OL,10,Fin Derby.
OL,12,FOn May 5 2023, he attacked two members
OL,13,Fof staff, who were a married couple,
OL,14,Fpunching the male colleague in the
OL,15,Fface before pushing over the female
OL,16,Fcolleague and hurting her leg, the
OL,17,Finquiry heard.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G2/5
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
