PN,37403
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F374A1773220132
OL,3,CKiller 'punched and pushed warehouse
OL,4,Cworkers' a month before Nottingham
OL,5,Cattacks
OL,7,FGiving evidence on Tuesday, a training
OL,8,Fcoordinator for the company at the
OL,9,Ftime, identified only as Louisa,
OL,10,Freferred to Calocane as 'VC': "We
OL,11,Fheard a scream from the back of the
OL,12,Fwarehouse.
OL,14,F"I then started to move in that
OL,15,Fdirection.
OL,17,F"The two victims ` the wife, she was
OL,18,Fin front of the husband, the husband
OL,19,Fwas already on the floor. He had
OL,20,Falready been assaulted.
OL,26,@rD@_OUvD@AOUyD@AOU
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G3/5
