PN,37404
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F374A1773220132
OL,3,CKiller 'punched and pushed warehouse
OL,4,Cworkers' a month before Nottingham
OL,5,Cattacks
OL,7,F"As I got into the area I stood myself
OL,8,Fin front of VC so my back would have
OL,9,Fbeen to the victims.
OL,11,F"VC was just stood in front of me,
OL,12,Fthere was no words coming out of VC's
OL,13,Fmouth.
OL,15,F"What was different is for the seconds
OL,16,FI was stood in front of VC his
OL,17,Fattention was not on me. He was
OL,18,Flooking through me and his attention
OL,19,Fwas on the male victim that was on the
OL,20,Ffloor."
OL,26,@oD@AOUsD@AOUwD@AOU|D@GO]
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G4/5
