PN,37405
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F374A1773220132
OL,3,CKiller 'punched and pushed warehouse
OL,4,Cworkers' a month before Nottingham
OL,5,Cattacks
OL,7,FShe said she remembers the male victim
OL,8,Fsaying he had been hit to the side of
OL,9,Fhis face, which had triggered an old
OL,10,Finjury, and that he did not know why
OL,11,Fhe had been attacked.
OL,13,FCalocane is currently detained
OL,14,Findefinitely in a high-security
OL,15,Fhospital after prosecutors accepted
OL,16,Fhis not guilty pleas to murder at his
OL,17,Fsentencing at Nottingham Crown Court
OL,18,Fin January 2024.
OL,20,FThe inquiry continues.
